data.text: PERSONAL: Versatile offensive lineman rated as one of the Top 18 players in Maryland and Top 50 offensive guards nationallyâ€¦four-star offensive lineman by Scout and PrepStar, earning All-Atlantic Region honorsâ€¦three-star offensive lineman by Rivals, ESPN and 247Sportsâ€¦rated the countryâ€™s 37th-best offensive guard by Scoutâ€¦ranked the No. 18 best player in the state of Maryland by Rivalsâ€¦rated the No. 39 offensive guard by ESPN and the 13th-best prospect in Maryland by ESPNâ€¦rated the No. 30 offensive guard and No. 11 player in Maryland by 247Sportsâ€¦earned Big School All-State First Team and Baltimore Sun All-Metro First Team honors for the second straight season as a senior helping Glenelg to its first state semifinals appearance since 2000 and anchoring an offensive line that featured two 1,000-yard rushersâ€¦selected All-Metro first team by the Baltimore Sun as a junior helping lead the way for a Glenelg offense that rushed for nearly 3,000 yards and won its first Howard County championship in a decadeâ€¦projected to play either guard or center in collegeâ€¦chose FSU over Maryland, Kentucky among other offers...born June 12, 1997.
